{"tid":625873,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解早餐唔食得飯 ?","createTime":"2018-04-11T19:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T18:35:37.000Z","uid":30006,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ca387d6674fd9748c775b3339b5fb73457cfa294","tid":625873,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"朝早行落街，唔係食通粉就係三文治飲咖啡，我唔明點解無碟頭飯食 ?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早餐食飯其實好撚正，特別有胃口食到飽一飽，成日都好有能量<br />\n<br />\n反為lunch 同 dinner 輕食，食下三文治果d ，中午唔使飯氣攻心恰眼訓，訓前唔使頂住個肚。<br />\n<br />\n好唔明點解香港人早午晚個份量係由小到大，甚至有人消夜大大份，而唔係調番轉，唔符合身體所需"},{"pid":"3f20eb10d1a603154e4840e0fae82ac8677ecbcc","tid":625873,"uid":126165,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:56:11.000Z","msg":"日本早餐係食飯<br />\n我自己都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5073cf1b7a845f2d128aafd6c18a7bae19cf0c22","tid":625873,"uid":30006,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"3f20eb10d1a603154e4840e0fae82ac8677ecbcc","tid":625873,"uid":126165,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:56:11.000Z","msg":"日本早餐係食飯<br />\n我自己都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:56:51.000Z","msg":"係，係日本早餐食個日本米飯，加個湯，有魚，真係人生一大享受"},{"pid":"4844cc32284de5016469798809060b3c5dbc1c4e","tid":625873,"uid":136302,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"早上趕頭趕命<br />\n夜晚放工緊係慰勞下自己"},{"pid":"6baffa9d9f26377d56214e07db4385831e6ab61d","tid":625873,"uid":30006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4844cc32284de5016469798809060b3c5dbc1c4e","tid":625873,"uid":136302,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"早上趕頭趕命<br />\n夜晚放工緊係慰勞下自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:58:30.000Z","msg":"早啲起身，早啲訓"},{"pid":"e04bfba6a0bdaff56eacd73a3f486b7b226dd588","tid":625873,"uid":136302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0